data.description: This 4 bedroom, brick ranch has something for every member of the family! Upon entering the kitchen you will find plenty of storage, a nice sized dining room and new carpet in the large living room complete with views of the backyard. Making your way down the hallway you will pass the first of 2 updated bathrooms on your way to the primary bedroom. Which boasts a walk-in closet with an ensuite that flows to the 3 additional ample size bedrooms. A finished, massive game room downstairs could be a 5th bedroom or the perfect entertaining space. The laundry room is large enough to use as additional storage space as well as the12x12 storage shed out back. Enjoy relaxing evenings or your morning coffee outside on either the front or rear covered porches. Complete with a fenced in front yard for your pets. The oversized (37x24ft) 2 car garage has infinite possibilities for all your projects. Welcome Home!
